    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for practical transportation with plenty of life left in it.",
