    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Every feature and electronic component works perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands the highest standard of quality and performance.",
