    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. It has significant mechanical issues, including an engine that fails to start and a transmission that requires a full overhaul. The exterior shows heavy wear with several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior has sustained considerable damage over the years. This car is ideal for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major restoration project or for someone in need of specific salvageable parts.",
